title: Fnatic started winning but now...

body:
Fnatic was one of the teams that had more support to start the competition, but after these last matches are not seeing what people wanted after chaining two consecutive defeats.
After the first victory, the team gave good impressions but after these last two games sensations are others and from my point of view not the favorites to win the world, I see that other teams like Origin and Skt who are most likely to title.
